headline: These Were the 3 Top-Performing Stocks in the Nasdaq-100 in August 2025
summary: The month of August was unremarkable for your average Nasdaq-100 stock -- with a few notable exceptions. These three stocks enjoyed more than 20% price gains in an otherwise sleepy 30-day period.
